'''Sandwasps''' were [[Insect/Legends|insects]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ord Cestus/Legends|Ord Cestus]].

During the [[Galactic War]], [[Ambassador/Legends|Ambassador]] [[Jannik (Human)|Jannik]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] once described the political situation in [[Voss-Ka]] to "a red-hot sandwasp hollow" in a message to a Republic hero.<ref name="Stirred up">{{TORcite|type=message|Stirred up|Ambassador Jannik}}</ref>

